snippet.title: My Sexuality | EP. 8 The Slumber Party ft. Patrick Starrr & Josh Leyva
snippet.description:
I’m Gay and That’s Okay! Episode 8 of #TheSlumberParty featuring Patrick Starrr and Josh Leyva. In this episode we’re talking about that topic many of us don’t really speak about: Sexuality. Learn more about how to find yourself and the meaning of love past physical touch. So what does sexual orientation mean to you and what impact has it had on your life? Take the quizzes and share your results by commenting below!!

----------------

Quiz Time!!!

1. What is your love language? 
(Gifts, Physical Touch, Words of Affirmation, Quality time, Acts of Service) http://www.5lovelanguages.com

2. What is your sex language? 
(Direct, Cat, Negotiator, Sensual, Mental)
